in just six years si spiegel and larry 
squarci have soared to the top of one of the christmas seasons most 
profitable industries the artificial tree 
hudson valley tree inc located in this city 60 miles north of 
new york city is one of the nations largest manufacturers of 
artificial christmas trees 
